# Copy to .env.local to switch the frontend from the built-in mock (localStorage)
# to the real backend.
#
# Leave UNSET  -> mock mode: the SPA runs standalone on localStorage.
# Set to /api  -> http mode: API calls go to the Node backend via the Vite proxy
#                 (run `npm run server` in another terminal, then `npm run dev`).
# You may also point it at a full URL, e.g. http://localhost:8787/api (CORS is on).

# VITE_API_BASE=/api
